verbose_text: We further determined that specific JNK1/2/3 inhibitor (SP600125) and specific ERK1/2 inhibitor (U0126) markedly inhibited the proliferation and migration of the SCAPs, consistent with the results that knockdown of GNAI3 inhibited the proliferation and migration of the SCAPs.
evidence: ERK1/2 inhibitor (U0126) markedly inhibited the proliferation and migration of the SCAPs
